1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:36,260 --> 00:00:43,060
(Lin Rulan's Grave)

3
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:45,000
(Lin Rulan's Grave)

4
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:46,520
(Lin Rulan's Grave)
Tomorrow is the anniversary of my death.

5
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:49,479
I'll enter the city as Lady Cheng'en.

6
00:00:50,159 --> 00:00:51,000
Mr. Liu.

7
00:00:51,439 --> 00:00:52,679
Tomorrow, in the city,

8
00:00:52,759 --> 00:00:53,920
please stir up the buzz for me.

9
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:56,079
If I can't leave the manor later,

10
00:00:56,079 --> 00:00:58,719
still help me pull this off in town.

11
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:00,759
Miss Rulan.

12
00:01:01,079 --> 00:01:02,359
The Yehu Gang and I

13
00:01:02,359 --> 00:01:04,239
will be your eyes and ears
in Jinxiu City.

14
00:01:04,599 --> 00:01:05,959
Act boldly without fear.

15
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:10,719
It's time to settle our score
with Wu Lian.

16
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,959
With her and Li Xiaoshou's help,

17
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:16,640
getting that list should be no problem.

18
00:01:20,599 --> 00:01:22,760
(Lin Rulan's Grave)
She remembers we love chestnut cakes.

19
00:01:28,180 --> 00:01:32,140
=Episode 3=

20
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,280
Master.

21
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,599
Everything is set up.

22
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,719
Word has spread through the city:

23
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:37,560
Lin Rulan's ghost is back for revenge.

24
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,920
She wants to pretend to be the Lady?

25
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:43,239
I'll make the whole city believe

26
00:01:43,239 --> 00:01:44,640
she's a vengeful ghost.

27
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,879
Let's see how she keeps up the act.

28
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:48,920
Enough.

29
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:50,159
Go back.

30
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:51,959
Yes, Master.

31
00:02:03,260 --> 00:02:06,079
(Yanyu Embroidery House)

32
00:02:06,079 --> 00:02:06,879
(Yanyu Embroidery House)
Lu silk.

33
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,680
Two taels, six qian per bolt.

34
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:11,800
Crimson ramie silk: four taels per bolt.

35
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:14,719
Most sold out right after the price hike.

36
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:16,960
You're deliberately targeting me!

37
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:19,599
(Huang Jiaojiao, Silk Thread's Owner)
Everyone knows I need crimson silk!

38
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:22,159
Jiaojiao, you misunderstand me.

39
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:24,199
Rumors say the city
is haunted last night.

40
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:27,120
People are buying red cloth
to ward off evil.

41
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,960
Yanyu Embroidery House selling cloth

42
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,319
is already an act of kindness.

43
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:34,879
Rumor says the ghost is Lin Rulan,

44
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:35,759
the embroideress you drove to death.

45
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:38,360
You even profit off
a ghost's misfortune!

46
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:40,159
Ms. Huang, don't talk nonsense.

47
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:43,599
Rulan came to me in a dream last night.

48
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:45,599
She said she's back

49
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:47,759
to thank Master for his teachings.

50
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,240
This handkerchief is proof.

51
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,599
Master Wu.

52
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:55,919
A female body was found
outside the city.

53
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,800
Likely Xiaoyi,
an embroiderer from your shop.

54
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:00,680
Please come identify the body with me.

55
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,639
It's Xiaoyi.

56
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,159
Since she was one of our embroiderers,

57
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:09,960
after the case is solved,

58
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,800
give her a proper burial on my behalf.

59
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,520
Yes, Master.

60
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,520
Wu Lian!

61
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,080
You killed another embroiderer!

62
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:18,960
(Wang Lu)
Liu Xin.

63
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,159
(Jinxiu City's Chief Constable)
You're no longer a constable.

64
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,360
Don't interfere with my investigation.

65
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,319
Wang Lu!

66
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,800
How did you get this position?

67
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,080
You know exactly how.

68
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,560
What did you do to Xiaoyi?

69
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,960
Xiaoyi snuck out last night

70
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,439
to meet a man secretly.

71
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,360
We reported it to Magistrate Yu.

72
00:03:34,439 --> 00:03:35,520
She's dead now.

73
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:37,599
You can slander her all you want.

74
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:40,280
That's exactly how you framed Rulan!

75
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,000
If she was pure,

76
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,560
no one could slander her.

77
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:45,000
Today, I'll see if your heart

78
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,280
is as rotten as your soul!

79
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:47,960
Liu Xin!

80
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,719
You dare kill in front of the Magistrate?

81
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:51,520
(Yu Ming, Magistrate of Jinxiu City)
Liu Xin!

82
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:53,759
You're no longer
in the government service.

83
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,639
Stop disrupting the investigation!

84
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,879
Step back! Now!

85
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:58,560
Your Honor!

86
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,439
Wu Lian framed me!

87
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:02,000
That's why I lost my job!

88
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,000
I don't care about that anymore!

89
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:06,240
This is a human life
we're talking about!

90
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,520
How can you let him get away
with murder?

91
00:04:09,159 --> 00:04:10,960
Have you been bribed too?

92
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:11,639
Guards!

93
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,840
Throw him in jail!

94
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,000
Lock him up for three days.

95
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:15,080
Take him away!

96
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:15,719
Yes.

97
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,199
Move!

98
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:24,759
Thank you for saving me, Your Honor.

99
00:04:24,759 --> 00:04:25,680
Master Wu.

100
00:04:26,639 --> 00:04:29,000
I'm up for a promotion soon.

101
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:32,800
Whoever committed this murder,

102
00:04:33,199 --> 00:04:36,360
I will handle it impartially.

103
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:39,279
Then please uphold justice

104
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:40,360
for Yanyu Embroidery House.

105
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:45,959
Thank goodness,
you had Magistrate Yu come early.

106
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,519
But there's one thing I don't get.

107
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:50,720
Why leave Xiaoyi's body

108
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:53,839
in the mass grave for Liu Xin to find?

109
00:04:54,439 --> 00:04:56,319
Master wanted him to watch

110
00:04:56,399 --> 00:04:57,639
Lin Rulan's old friend

111
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:59,720
die helpless right in front of him.

112
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,000
(Wu Xin, Wu Lian's Errand Boy)
What a pity.

113
00:05:01,199 --> 00:05:02,600
It's only three days in jail.

114
00:05:02,879 --> 00:05:03,720
Three days?

115
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,079
Three days is more than enough.

116
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,839
The Princess Consort orders:

117
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:10,839
You have traveled far

118
00:05:10,839 --> 00:05:12,079
and are unwell.

119
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,839
Please stay in your private courtyard
these days.

120
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:16,000
After the virginity check,

121
00:05:16,199 --> 00:05:18,240
the Prince will return for the wedding.

122
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,000
No way!

123
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,639
This is an insult!

124
00:05:20,959 --> 00:05:22,600
This is royal etiquette.

125
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,879
You wouldn't understand.

126
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,120
But Your Lady will understand.

127
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:28,319
Nanny Du.

128
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,879
I want to go to the garden.

129
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:31,120
Is that forbidden too?

130
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,879
Calm down, My Lady.

131
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:35,399
The Princess Consort means well.

132
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:37,279
Or perhaps,

133
00:05:38,079 --> 00:05:40,319
do you have secrets

134
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,319
the Princess Consort doesn't know?

135
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,839
If she means well,

136
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,360
then I'll do as she says.

137
00:05:56,399 --> 00:05:57,279
Mr. Liu.

138
00:05:58,639 --> 00:06:00,079
This cell looks much nicer

139
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,120
than the one you had

140
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:04,240
three years ago.

141
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,079
What do you want?

142
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,079
To turn yourself in?

143
00:06:07,639 --> 00:06:08,560
Liu Xin.

144
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,959
My patience has limits.

145
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,600
If you keep causing trouble
over Lin Rulan,

146
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:17,759
I won't mind
killing a dead person twice.

147
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,399
Don't you dare touch her!

148
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:27,519
Looks like our former constable
still hasn't learned his lesson.

149
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:29,120
Wang Lu.

150
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:29,839
Yes, Master.

151
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:31,560
Cut off one of his fingers.

152
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,600
Teach him a lesson.

153
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,800
Yes, Master.

154
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,240
Wu Lian!

155
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:39,000
Kill me if you have the guts!

156
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:40,759
If you don't kill me today,

157
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,040
I'll watch you every single day.

158
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,639
I'll bury you sooner or later!

159
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:46,920
Look at him, like a rabid dog.

160
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,040
Wu Lian!

161
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:53,120
Wu Lian's subtle hints

162
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:55,120
actually made Her Highness suspicious.

163
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,279
Our top priority now

164
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,720
is to find a way

165
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,920
to pass the virginity check.

166
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,240
Let's go find Mr. Liu.

167
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,480
My Lady.

168
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:05,519
My Lady, bad news!

169
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,759
Mr. Liu has been locked up!

170
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,399
No!

171
00:07:08,879 --> 00:07:10,279
I have to see him right now!

172
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:11,839
Xiaojiu, Xiaotao.

173
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:12,720
Here's the plan.

174
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:22,199
My Lady.

175
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,399
Where are you going?

176
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:28,319
Ruoheng, at a time like this,

177
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:30,480
why cover your face?

178
00:07:30,839 --> 00:07:31,560
My Lady.

179
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:34,199
Just tell Her Highness the truth.

180
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,680
She's a forgiving person.

181
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:41,839
No.

182
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,240
That's impossible.

183
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,519
What's going on?

184
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:47,439
Your Highness, My Lady is sorry!

185
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:49,680
She was upset today

186
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,800
after being wronged.

187
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:52,759
She bribed the guards

188
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,360
and snuck to the lotus pond

189
00:07:54,639 --> 00:07:56,959
to release a koi fish for good luck.

190
00:07:57,399 --> 00:08:01,199
You snuck out at night just for a koi?

191
00:08:01,399 --> 00:08:04,560
Why not release it inside the manor?

192
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,800
Nanny, you're being foolish.

193
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:08,519
Koi from this manor

194
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:10,920
must be released outside the manor.

195
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:13,399
What you said
is just releasing them locally.

196
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:16,519
Ask the two bribed guards

197
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,680
if you don't believe me.

198
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:19,680
Then why are you doing this?

199
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:20,920
Where is your Lady?

200
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:22,800
It's the middle of the night.

201
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,879
My Lady is fast asleep.

202
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,319
So of course

203
00:08:26,519 --> 00:08:28,800
I, her head maid, handled this.

204
00:08:32,399 --> 00:08:33,919
We fell for a diversion!

205
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:36,000
Let's do the virginity check now.

206
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,360
Catch her off guard.

207
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:40,360
Can we get the midwife this late?

208
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,399
She's on the royal payroll.

209
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,440
We can summon her anytime.

210
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:44,840
Oh no!

211
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,679
I hope My Lady makes it back in time.

212
00:08:47,639 --> 00:08:48,080
My Lady.

213
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,720
Let go of me!

214
00:08:48,799 --> 00:08:49,639
My Lady.

215
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,639
Her Highness needs you urgently.

216
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:52,840
Please get up, My Lady.

217
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:53,759
No!

218
00:08:53,799 --> 00:08:55,159
Please get up, My Lady.

219
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,720
Behave yourself!

220
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,840
Let go! Who are you?

221
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,519
Get out!

222
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,039
Don't move!

223
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:05,000
Only the Princess Consort
rules Jingyuan Manor!

224
00:09:05,039 --> 00:09:05,720
Behave!

225
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:06,480
How dare you!

226
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:09,000
I'll tell my cousin,
and you'll be punished!

227
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,919
Shut up!

228
00:09:16,039 --> 00:09:16,440
My Lady.

229
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,039
Your Highness,

230
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,039
the check is done.

231
00:09:18,159 --> 00:09:19,200
She is a virgin.

232
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,159
Are you absolutely sure?

233
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,559
Yes, Your Highness.

234
00:09:22,639 --> 00:09:24,200
I serve the royal family.

235
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,240
I would never lie

236
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,159
to Your Highness.

237
00:09:26,559 --> 00:09:27,279
You may leave.

238
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:28,320
Yes, Your Highness.

239
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,679
Wenyue.

240
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:41,080
If you didn't trust me,

241
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,639
you never should have sent for me.

242
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:44,519
I put aside our childhood bond

243
00:09:45,039 --> 00:09:48,200
to trust you and marry to the Prince.

244
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,240
And yet you...

245
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:52,639
Even if you don't care
about our sisterhood,

246
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:55,240
you should respect my family's honor!

247
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:59,039
I can't face my parents now!

248
00:09:59,039 --> 00:10:00,480
My Lady! My Lady!

249
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,720
Don't do anything rash!

250
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,039
If the Prince finds out,

251
00:10:03,039 --> 00:10:04,200
he'll be heartbroken.

252
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,200
Nonsense.

253
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:07,840
Ruoheng.

254
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,720
This is royal protocol.

255
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,480
Don't blame me for this.

256
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,960
It breaks my heart to see you like this.

257
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:16,399
It's all those villains' fault.

258
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,240
They sowed discord

259
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,159
and caused this trouble.

260
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,960
I'll teach them a lesson right now

261
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:22,840
to make it up to you.

262
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:24,919
Nanny Du.

263
00:10:25,159 --> 00:10:26,799
Go reprimand Wu Lian on my behalf.

264
00:10:27,039 --> 00:10:28,320
If he causes trouble again,

265
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:29,919
I will punish him severely.

266
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:30,840
Yes, Your Highness.

267
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,519
Wu Lian.

268
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:40,080
Making the Princess Consort
turn against you

269
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:42,159
is just the first step.

270
00:11:14,140 --> 00:11:17,100
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

271
00:11:17,340 --> 00:11:20,340
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

272
00:11:21,540 --> 00:11:24,300
♪The past no longer binds♪

273
00:11:24,780 --> 00:11:28,500
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

274
00:11:28,940 --> 00:11:33,060
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

275
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:36,780
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

276
00:11:37,140 --> 00:11:39,140
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

277
00:11:39,140 --> 00:11:43,220
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

278
00:11:43,620 --> 00:11:45,820
♪For your faith that never broke♪

279
00:11:46,020 --> 00:11:50,140
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

280
